      • check

        public void check(Patient patient)
        This is used to take a patient from the WaitinQueue to the BloodTestRoom.
        The room state is set to full and the patient state is set to checked.
        Parameters:
        patient - The patient which is going to undergo a bloodtest

      • endCheck

        public void endCheck(Patient patient)
        At the end of the test, the patient is set to "waitingForVerdict", and the room to "empty" The patient is relocated to the waiting room and a message is sent to the physician. Finally, the patient is billed.
        Parameters:
        patient - The patient finishing this bloodtest
